'''芙蕾达·赛-{}-琳娜·平托'''（{{lang-hi|फ्रीडा पिंटो}}、{{lang-en|Freida Selena Pinto}}，{{bd|1984年|10月18日|catIdx=P}}）是一名主要在美国和英国电影中演出的印度女演员。她在印度孟买出生并长大，很小时就立志要当演员。就读孟买圣沙勿略学院期间，她曾参与业余戏剧演出。毕业后，她还短暂从事过模特和电视节目主持人的工作。

平托因2008年的英国剧情片《[[贫民窟的百万富翁|贫民窟的百万富翁]]》一炮走红，并以这部电影处女作赢得[[棕榈泉国际电影节|棕榈泉国际电影节]]最具突破演出奖，还获得[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]、[[MTV电影大奖|MTV电影大奖]]和[[青少年选择奖|青少年选择奖]]提名。接下来她又在多部美国和英国电影中亮相，大多是出演配角。她在商业上最成功的作品是2011年的[[科幻电影|科幻片]]《[[猩球崛起|猩球崛起]]》。2011年，平托因在[[迈克尔·温特伯顿|迈克尔·温特伯顿]]执导的《[[特莉萨娜|特莉萨娜]]》中扮演电影同名女主角获得广泛关注。2014年，她又因出演传记片《[[沙漠舞者|沙漠舞者]]》获得评论界好评。

虽然印度媒体称赞平托在外国电影中打破印度女性的[[刻板印象|刻板形象]]，但她本人在印度影坛的知名度不高。从影後，她还投身人道主义事业，并为女性和儿童权利代言。

== 早年经历和背景 ==
芙蕾达·赛-{}-琳娜·平托于1984年10月18日在印度孟买出生<ref name="tribune">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060421/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2009/20090309/ttlife1.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.tribuneindia.com/2009/20090309/ttlife1.htm | title = Woman behind success | work = The Tribune (Chandigarh) | agency = Indo-Asian News Service | date = 2009-03-09 | accessdate = 2016-06-28}}</ref>，父母都是[[门格洛尔天主教徒|门格洛尔天主教徒]]{{efn|平托曾在接受《[[访问_(杂志)|访问]]》杂志采访时称：“我来自印度南部的门格洛尔，那里有很多天主教徒。他们中有些人是在英国或葡萄牙治下被迫改信天主教，所以我很可能没有天主教血统，或许就是印度的印度教徒。”<ref name="Stylist">{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto's identity crisis | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404063304/http://www.stylist.co.uk/people/freida-pintos-identity-crisis | deadurl = no | url = http://www.stylist.co.uk/people/freida-pintos-identity-crisis | work = Stylist | accessdate = 2016-06-28 | quote = I come from Mangalore, which is in the southern part of India, where you have a big Catholic population. Some of them were forced into conversions by the British and Portuguese. So I may not necessarily have that kind of lineage. I could pretty much be a Hindu from India...}}</ref>}}，源自过去属葡萄牙殖民地的[[果阿邦|果阿邦]]<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203020952/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-slumdog-has-done-india-proud-says-frieda-s-father-1233560 | title = Slumdog has done India proud, says Freida's father | work = Daily News and Analysis | url = http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-slumdog-has-done-india-proud-says-frieda-s-father-1233560 | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | date = 2009-02-23 | accessdate = 2016-06-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/freida-pinto-1#_ | title = Freida Pinto | last = Blanks | first = Tim | work = [[访问_(杂志)|Interview]] | date = 2011-07-25 | accessdate = 2016-06-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324041610/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/freida-pinto-1/#_ | archivedate = 2016-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto wants to undergo DNA test to prove she is Indian | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2011-07-25 | accessdate = 2016-06-28 | archivedate = 2015-07-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708054718/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/film-news/8658314/Freida-Pinto-wants-to-undergo-DNA-test-to-prove-she-is-Indian.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/film-news/8658314/Freida-Pinto-wants-to-undergo-DNA-test-to-prove-she-is-Indian.html}}</ref>。她的父亲弗雷德里克·平托（{{lang|en|Frederick Pinto}}）是[[巴罗达银行|巴罗达银行]]的分行高级经理，母亲西尔维亚·平托（{{lang|en|Sylvia Pinto}}）则是孟买[[戈雷加奥恩_(孟买)|戈雷加奥恩]]（{{lang|en|Goregaon}}）圣约翰高中的校长。芙蕾达还有个名叫莎朗（{{lang|en|Sharon}}）的姐姐，在[[新德里电视台|新德里电视台]]上班<ref name="daj">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331171738/http://www.daijiworld.com/news/news_disp.asp?n_id=53994 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.daijiworld.com/news/news_disp.asp?n_id=53994 |title=The Newest Star on the Mangalorean Horizon – Freida Pinto |last=D'Mello |first=Gerry |publisher=Daijiworld Media |date=2008-11-25 |accessdate=2016-06-28 |archivedate=2016-03-31 }}</ref>。

[[File:Xaviers_college.jpg|thumbnail]]

平托在[[马拉德_(孟买)|马拉德]]（{{lang|en|Malad}}）长大，家中[[印度生活水准|生活水准]]达到中产阶级水平<ref name="NYT">{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto opens up about a "crime against a woman's body" in India | last1 = Thacker | first1 = Purvi | last2 = Katz | first2 = Brigit | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 2015-04-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160220041901/http://nytlive.nytimes.com/womenintheworld/2015/04/10/freida-pinto-opens-up-about-her-advocacy-efforts-for-girls/ | accessdate = 2016-06-28 | archivedate = 2016-02-20 | deadurl = yes | url = http://nytlive.nytimes.com/womenintheworld/2015/04/10/freida-pinto-opens-up-about-her-advocacy-efforts-for-girls/ }}</ref><ref name="MumbaiMirror">{{cite news |accessdate=2016-06-28 |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20151107071326/http://www.mumbaimirror.com/mumbai/cover-story/Freidas-secret-shoot-at-Chakala-for-Holly-biggie/articleshow/16118381.cms |deadurl=no |url=http://www.mumbaimirror.com/mumbai/cover-story/Freidas-secret-shoot-at-Chakala-for-Holly-biggie/articleshow/16118381.cms |title=Freida's secret shoot at Chakala for Holly biggie |work=Mumbai Mirror |date=2011-04-16 |archivedate=2015-11-07 }}</ref>。早在五岁那样，她就想成为演员<ref name="IE1">{{cite news | accessdate = 2016-06-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208155607/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/freida-pinto-wanted-to-be-a-michael-jackson-impersonator/716431/ | title = Freida Pinto wanted to be a Michael Jackson impersonator | work = The Indian Express | url = http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/freida-pinto-wanted-to-be-a-michael-jackson-impersonator/716431/ | deadurl = no | date = 2010-11-26 | archivedate = 2015-12-08}}</ref><ref name="telegraph">{{cite news | accessdate = 2016-06-28 | url = http://www.telegraphindia.com/1090302/jsp/entertainment/story_10610538.jsp | title = There's nothing to be so kicked about, girl! it's just luck by chance | last = Roy | first = Priyanka | work = The Telegraph (Calcutta) | date = 2009-03-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304215524/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1090302/jsp/entertainment/story_10610538.jsp | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，童年时经常打扮自己模仿电视中的演员<ref name="IE1" /><ref name="audrey">{{cite journal |url=http://www.audreymagazine.com/index.php?element=cover_story&archive=409 |title=Destiny's Child |last=Sung |first=Helena |issue=February – March 2009 |accessdate=2010-01-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5miiHLKx6?url=http://www.audreymagazine.com/index.php?element=cover_story |archivedate=2010-01-12 |work=Audrey (magazine) }}</ref>。据平托回忆，[[苏丝米塔·森|苏丝米塔·森]]赢得[[1994年环球小姐|1994年环球小姐]]桂冠令她深受启发，“整个国家都为她深感自豪，当时我就想，总有一天我也要像她那样<ref name="NYTimes">{{cite news | title = Out on a Limb | last = Silva | first = Horacio | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151104155728/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/08/22/t-magazine/22well-coverstory-t.html | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2010/08/22/t-magazine/22well-coverstory-t.html?_r=0 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2010-08-19 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2015-11-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。”平托先是在马拉德的圣若瑟卡梅尔修道院女校就读<ref name="Rego">{{cite news | title = Unplugged: Freida Pinto | last = Rego | first = Norbert | work = The Times of India | date = 2009-10-21 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2009-09-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090905161814/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/people/Unplugged-Freida-Pinto/articleshow/4379041.cms | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/people/Unplugged-Freida-Pinto/articleshow/4379041.cms}}</ref>，然后获孟买圣沙勿略学院录取，主修[[英语文学|英语文学]]，辅修[[心理学|心理学]]和[[经济学|经济学]]<ref name="audrey" /><ref name="rediff">{{cite web | url = http://www.rediff.com/movies/2008/jun/16slid1.htm | title = It's natural to want to become an actress after living in Mumbai | last = Ramani | first = Nithya | publisher = Rediff.com | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075457/http://www.rediff.com/movies/2008/jun/16slid1.htm | deadurl = no}}</ref>。高校求学期间，她曾参与[[业余戏剧演出|业余戏剧演出]]<ref name="audrey" />，但一直等到2005年毕业后才开始接受表演和模特工作邀约<ref name="Steve">{{cite news | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/mar/01/frieda-pinto-i-feel-timid | title = Freida Pinto on being Tess | last = Rose | first = Steve | work = The Guardian | date = 2012-03-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305070413/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/mar/01/frieda-pinto-i-feel-timid | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | accessdate = 2016-06-29}}</ref>。

虽然年幼时就立志投身表演事业，但平托直到上大学时看过《[[女魔头|女魔头]]》后才决定从影。对此她表示：“那时候我应该是看了《女魔头》……然后就下了决心。我一定要找到门路，一定要有这种彻底转型的作品。”<ref name="interviewtwo">{{cite web | url = http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/freida-pinto-1/#page3 | title = Freida Pinto | last = Blanks | first = Tim | work = Interview | date = 2011-07-25 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324041610/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/freida-pinto-1/#page3 | archivedate = 2016-03-24}}</ref>。平托的模特生涯于2005年开始，并于同年加入印度[[精锐模特管理公司|精锐模特管理公司]]<ref name="tribune" />并合作两年半<ref name="audrey" />。她在多个电视或平面广告亮相，涉及产品包括[[箭牌|箭牌口香糖]]、[[斯柯达汽车|斯柯达汽车]]、[[印度沃达丰|印度沃达丰]]、[[巴帝电信|巴帝电信]]、{{lang|en|[[Visa|Visa]]}}、{{lang|en|[[eBay|eBay]]}}和[[戴比尔斯|戴比尔斯]]<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160423173919/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/faces-to-look-forward-in-2009/freida-pinto-slumdog-millionaire/slideshow/3937916.cms | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | work = The Economic Times | deadurl = no | url = http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/faces-to-look-forward-in-2009/freida-pinto-slumdog-millionaire/slideshow/3937916.cms | title = Freida Pinto – Slumdog Millionaire | date = 2009-01-05 | archivedate = 2016-04-23}}</ref>。

从事模特工作期间，平托还开始参加电影和电视节目试镜，获选担任国际旅游节目《完整循环》（{{lang|en|''Full Circle''}}）的主持人，节目于2006至2008年间在[[Zee_TV|Zee亚太国际频道]]播出<ref name="telegraph" />。借主持节目之机，平托得以前往包括阿富汗、斐济、马来西亚、新加坡和泰国在内的多个国家<ref name="Tzanelli" />。她还参加过多部[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]和[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]电影试镜，如争取出演[[马克·福斯特|马克·福斯特]]执导的《[[007：大破量子危机|007：大破量子危机]]》中[[邦德女郎|邦德女郎]]卡米尔·蒙特斯（{{lang|en|Camille Montes}}）一角，但这些尝试大多落空<ref name="audrey" /><ref name="interviewtwo" /><ref name="Tzanelli" />。据平托之后回忆，这些经历让她学到很多经验，她“很高兴事情是这样发展。我需要被拒绝，需要学习，事情就该如此……我能接受100次拒绝，相信一定会有某个特别的机会注定要落在我头上<ref name="interview">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220548/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/freida-pinto/#_ | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/freida-pinto/#_ | title = Freida Pinto | last = Martin | first = Michael | work = Interview | date = 2010-11-05 | accessdate = 2016-06-29}}</ref>。”

== 演艺生涯 ==

=== 2008至2010年：起步和突破 ===
[[File:Slumdog_Millionaire_screening_at_Ryerson_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
2007年，平托所在的模特经纪公司应《[[贫民窟的百万富翁|贫民窟的百万富翁]]》选角主任要求挑选七名模特参加该片女主角试镜，平托便是其中之一<ref name="tribune" /><ref name="audrey" />。经过长达六个月的反复试镜，平托赢得角色，在片中饰演男主角杰玛（{{lang|en|Jamal}}）的心上人拉媞卡（{{lang|en|Latika}}），与[[戴夫·帕特尔|戴夫·帕特尔]]演对手戏<ref name="theguardian2009">{{cite news | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/jan/03/slumdog-millionaire-stars | title = Desi mates | last = Hubert | first = Andrea | work = The Guardian | date = 2009-01-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305085253/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/jan/03/slumdog-millionaire-stars | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05}}</ref>。电影后期制作期间，她在孟买的[[巴里·约翰_(导演)|巴里·约翰表演工作室]]学习表演课程<ref name="daj" />。虽然从课程中可以学到表演的“技术方面”知识，但平托觉得结合实际经验来看，这些知识“同实际演出截然不同……所以对我来说，最有用的表演学习经历就是在[[丹尼·博伊尔|丹尼·博伊尔]]手下试镜那六个月<ref name="audrey" />。”《贫民窟的百万富翁》成为2008年世界影坛的黑马，其剧情和配乐广受好评<ref name="Huber-Warring2010">{{cite book | title = Storied Inquiries in International Landscapes: An Anthology of Educational Research | last = Huber-Warring | first = Tonya | page = 511 | year = 2010 | publisher = Information Age Publishing | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=p4iml45o3boC&pg=PA511&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | isbn = 978-1-60752-395-6 | archive-date = 2016-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818105912/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=p4iml45o3boC&pg=PA511&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | date = 2009-01-20 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305055646/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2009/jan/20/slumdog-millionaire-sleeper-hit | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2009/jan/20/slumdog-millionaire-sleeper-hit | title = Slumdog Millionaire is the UK's biggest ever sleeper hit | last = Gant | first = Charles | work = The Guardian | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，以1500万美元预算获得3.77亿美元全球票房<ref>{{cite web | title = Slumdog Millionaire | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160606174214/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=slumdogmillionaire.htm | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2016-06-06 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=slumdogmillionaire.htm}}</ref>，也是[[第81届奥斯卡金像奖|第81届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中最成功的电影，全部十项提名有八项获奖，其中包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片奖]]<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151120184403/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/oscars/4784569/Oscars-2009-Slumdog-Millionaire-wins-eight-Academy-Awards-including-best-picture-and-best-director.html | archivedate = 2015-11-20 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/oscars/4784569/Oscars-2009-Slumdog-Millionaire-wins-eight-Academy-Awards-including-best-picture-and-best-director.html | title = Oscars 2009: Slumdog Millionaire wins eight Academy Awards including best picture and best director | last = Elsworth | first = Catherine | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2009-02-23 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。平托本人在[[棕榈泉国际电影节|棕榈泉国际电影节]]上获最具突破演出奖，并同片中其他演员一起夺得[[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会奖]][[美国演员工会奖最佳群体演出奖|最佳群体演出奖]]<ref name="PS" /><ref name="IBN" />，她还因出演本片在[[第62届英国电影学院奖|第62届英国电影学院奖]]角逐中获[[英国电影学院奖最佳女配角|最佳女配角奖]]提名<ref name="bafta">{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/2009,2378,BA.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831154107/http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/2009%2C2378%2CBA.html |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2014-08-31 |title=Film Awards Winners in 2009 |publisher=British Academy of Film and Television Arts |accessdate=2014-08-31 }}</ref>。平托在电影中的出场时间有限，所以没有引起多少评论界关注。《[[加尔各答电信报|加尔各答电信报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Telegraph''}}）认为这么少的戏份让人难以对她的演技作出判断，该报专栏作家巴拉什·普拉丹（{{lang|en|Bharathi S. Pradhan}}）指出，“《贫民窟的百万富翁》还不足以考验芙蕾达的表演实力<ref name="telegraph" />。”

