凭《贫民窟的百万富翁》打响名气后，平托又签约出演两部文艺电影<ref name="reutersapes">{{cite news | last = Blair | first = Iain | title = Freida Pinto rises up in new 'Planet of the Apes' | archivedate = 2016-03-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160314085559/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-freidapinto-idUSTRE7735IZ20110804 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/us-freidapinto-idUSTRE7735IZ20110804 | agency = Reuters | date = 2011-08-04 | accessdate = 2016-06-29}}</ref><ref name="independent">{{cite news | title = Slumdog to stardom: How Freida Pinto has adapted to the demands of fame | work = The Independent | date = 2011-07-13 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121024330/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/slumdog-to-stardom-how-freida-pinto-has-adapted-to-the-demands-of-fame-2326905.html | archivedate = 2015-11-21 | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/slumdog-to-stardom-how-freida-pinto-has-adapted-to-the-demands-of-fame-2326905.html}}</ref>。一部是[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]执导的喜剧片《[[遭遇陌生人|遭遇陌生人]]》（{{lang|en|''You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger''}}）<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/22/movies/22you.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | title = Looking for Something When Life Signifies Nothing | last = Scott | first = A. O. | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2010-09-21 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2015-05-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150505011732/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/22/movies/22you.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0}}</ref>，她在片中与[[安东尼奥·班德拉斯|安东尼奥·班德拉斯]]、[[乔许·布洛林|乔许·布洛林]]、[[安东尼·霍普金斯|安东尼·霍普金斯]]、[[阿努潘·凯尔|阿努潘·凯尔]]（{{lang|en|Anupam Kher}}）和[[娜奥米·沃茨|娜奥米·沃茨]]合作演出<ref name="sukanya">{{cite web | date = 2010-12-17 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | url = http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/review-you-will-meet-a-tall-dark-stranger/20101217.htm | title = A twisted Woody Allen fairytale! | last = Verma | first = Sukanya | publisher = Rediff.com | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222822/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/review-you-will-meet-a-tall-dark-stranger/20101217.htm}}</ref>，饰演身份不明的“神秘女性”，引起布洛林扮演角色的关注。影片于2010年5月在[[第63届戛纳电影节|第63届戛纳电影节]]首映，正式上映后所获评价褒贬不一。<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305215327/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/you-will-meet-a-tall-dark-stranger | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/you-will-meet-a-tall-dark-stranger | title = You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger | publisher = Metacritic | accessdate = 2016-06-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/you_will_meet_a_tall_dark_stranger/ | archivedate = 2016-04-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160423155345/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/you_will_meet_a_tall_dark_stranger/ | title = You Will Meet a Tall, Dark Stranger (2010)}}</ref>接下来平托又在[[朱利安·许纳贝|朱利安·许纳贝]]导演的《[[米拉尔|米拉尔]]》（{{lang|en|''Miral''}}）中出镜，该片根据[[露拉·耶布瑞尔|露拉·耶布瑞尔]]（{{lang|en|Rula Jebreal}}）的[[自传体小说|半自传体小说]]改编，平托的角色是在以色列难民营长大的巴勒斯坦孤儿<ref name="roles">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160629163339/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/nri-entertainment/Freidas-freed-herself-from-desi-stereotypes/articleshow/13640190.cms | title = Freida's freed herself from desi stereotypes | last = Joshi | first = Tushar | work = The Times of India | date = 2012-05-30 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2016-06-29 | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/nri-entertainment/Freidas-freed-herself-from-desi-stereotypes/articleshow/13640190.cms}}</ref>。电影在巴勒斯坦领地摄制，平托此前还专门探访当地多个难民营，为演出做准备<ref name="LATmiral">{{cite news | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2011/mar/27/entertainment/la-ca-freida-pinto-20110327 | title = Miral's Freida Pinto aims for a global takeover | last = Adams | first = Sam | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2011-03-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307143632/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/mar/27/entertainment/la-ca-freida-pinto-20110327 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-29}}</ref>。她还表示，20世纪40年代[[印巴分治|印巴分治]]期间她也有过类似经历，所以更能理解主人翁的性格特点<ref name="LATmiral" />。影评人对《米拉尔》的整体感观不佳<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/miral | title = Miral (2010) | publisher = Metacritic | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160315014756/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/miral | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miral/ | title = Miral (2010) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160412020354/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miral/ | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-12 | accessdate = 2016-06-30}}</ref>，但对平托表演的态度呈两极分化状态<ref>{{cite web | last = J Pais | first = Arthur | title = Freida Pinto gets good reviews for Miral | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304123406/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/freida-pinto-gets-good-reviews-for-miral/20110322.htm | url = http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/freida-pinto-gets-good-reviews-for-miral/20110322.htm | publisher = Rediff.com | date = 2011-03-22 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。《[[独立报|独立报]]》的杰弗里·麦克纳布（{{lang|en|Geoffrey Macnab}}）认为平托对米拉尔一角的诠释“非常引人入胜”<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221055/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/miral-venice-film-festival-2069079.html | title = Miral, Venice Film Festival | work = The Independent | last = Macnab | first = Geoffrey | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/miral-venice-film-festival-2069079.html | date = 2010-09-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但《[[卫报|卫报]]》的[[彼得·布拉德肖|彼得·布拉德肖]]（{{lang|en|Peter Bradshaw}}）则感觉平托在片中“看起来心神不宁，似乎不适合出演这个角色<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305052542/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/dec/02/miral-review | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/dec/02/miral-review | title = Miral – review | last = Bradshaw | first = Peter | work = The Guardian | date = 2010-12-02 | accessdate = 2016-06-30}}</ref>。”

=== 2011年后 ===
2011年有四部平托参演的电影上映，首先是《[[人猿星球|人猿星球]]》系列电影的[[重启|重启]]之作、科幻片《[[猩球崛起|猩球崛起]]》<ref>{{cite news | last = Bagdadi | first = Danish | title = All 8 'The Planet of the Apes' Movies Ranked from Worst to Best | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151219110416/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/comment-all-8-the-planet-of-the-apes-movies-ranked-from-worst-to-best-2001648 | work = Daily News and Analysis | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | url = http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/comment-all-8-the-planet-of-the-apes-movies-ranked-from-worst-to-best-2001648 | date = 2014-07-12 | archivedate = 2015-12-19}}</ref>。她在片中饰演[[灵长类学|灵长类学家]]卡罗琳（{{lang|en|Caroline}}），是[[詹姆斯·弗兰科|詹姆斯·弗兰科]]出演角色的恋人<ref name="roles" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto out of 'Planet of the Apes' sequel | work = Mid Day | date = 2013-06-04 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072610/http://www.mid-day.com/articles/freida-pinto-out-of-planet-of-the-apes-sequel/216467 | url = http://www.mid-day.com/articles/freida-pinto-out-of-planet-of-the-apes-sequel/216467 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。为了演好角色，她还花时间钻研英格兰[[人类学|人类学家]][[珍·古道尔|珍·古道尔]]的事业发展历程<ref name="reutersapes" />。影片的全球票房总额达4亿8180万美元，截至2016年6月依然是她票房最高的作品<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Actor&id=freidapinto.htm | title = Freida Pinto: Worldwide (Unadjusted) | publisher = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-04-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160417110100/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Actor&id=freidapinto.htm | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不过，平托的角色因人物形象太单一而受到批评，安东尼·昆（{{lang|en|Anthony Quinn}}）在《独立报》撰文称这是电影失败的一面<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305021114/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/rise-of-the-planet-of-the-apes-12a-2336016.html | title = Rise of the Planet of the Apes (12A) | last = Quinn | first = Anthony | deadurl = no | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/rise-of-the-planet-of-the-apes-12a-2336016.html | work = The Independent | date = 2011-10-23}}</ref>，《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》的[[托德·麦卡锡|托德·麦卡锡]]（{{lang|en|Todd McCarthy}}）觉得这不过又是银幕上已延续存在多年的又一个端庄女友形象，并且无聊程度更胜往昔<ref>{{cite web | last = McCarthy | first = Todd | date = 2011-08-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | title = Rise of the Planet of the Apes: Film Review | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151211171915/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/rise-planet-apes-film-review-218819 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/rise-planet-apes-film-review-218819 | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archivedate = 2015-12-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。接下来平托在[[迈克尔·温特伯顿|迈克尔·温特伯顿]]导演的《特莉萨娜》（{{lang|en|''Trishna''}}）中饰演电影同名女主角。影片根据[[托马斯·哈代|托马斯·哈代]]的小说《[[德伯家的苔丝|德伯家的苔丝]]》改编，平托的角色是[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]]农家少女，离开家人前去为英国出生的印度酒店业主打工，与[[里兹·阿迈德|里兹·阿迈德]]演对手戏<ref name="Philip">{{cite news | last = French | first = Philip | title = Slumdog Millionaire star Freida Pinto captivates in Michael Winterbottom's bold reading of Hardy's tragedy | work = The Guardian | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160603014547/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/mar/11/trishna-michael-winterbottom-review | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/mar/11/trishna-michael-winterbottom-review | archivedate = 2016-06-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Collin | first = Robbie | title = Trishna, review | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/9131922/Trishna-review.html | date = 2012-03-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160326114559/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/9131922/Trishna-review.html | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。电影在[[2011年多伦多电影节首映|2011年多伦多电影节首映]]，评论界反响褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web | title = Trishna | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/trishna | publisher = Metacritic | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archive-date = 2015-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203193921/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/trishna | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160423143854/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trishna_2011/ | title = Trishna (2012) | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trishna_2011/ | archivedate = 2016-04-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《今日印度》（{{lang|en|''India Today''}}）的尼沙特·巴里（{{lang|en|Nishat Bari}}）称赞这是平托当时“最扎实”的演出<ref>{{cite web | last = BBari | first = Nishat | title = Freida Pinto: Ticket to Hollywood | work = India Today | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160406223838/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/india-today-youth-special-freida-pinto-ticket-to-hollywood/1/151584.html | archivedate = 2016-04-06 | date = 2011-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | url = http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/india-today-youth-special-freida-pinto-ticket-to-hollywood/1/151584.html}}</ref>。[[菲利普·法兰奇|菲利普·法兰奇]]（{{lang|en|Philip French}}）则在《卫报》撰文称平托扮演的女主角“令人着迷”<ref name="Philip" />，《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]也称赞她的演出“美得令人感动”<ref>{{cite news | last = Ebert | first = Roger | author-link = 罗杰·埃伯特 | title = Trishna | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/trishna-2012 | publisher = rogerebert.com | date = 2012-07-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063821/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/trishna-2012 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。不过，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的[[玛诺拉·达吉斯|玛诺拉·达吉斯]]（{{lang|en|Manohla Dargis}}）对此有不同看法，在她看来，平托虽是片中“最美丽的风景之一，但她和导演都没有给予特莉萨娜足够的生命力<ref>{{cite news|last=Dargis |first=Manhola |title=A Little Bollywood Flavors This 'Tess' |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/13/movies/trishna-from-michael-winterbottom-starring-freida-pinto.html |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2012-07-12 |accessdate=2016-06-29 |archivedate=2012-09-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120901212542/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/13/movies/trishna-from-michael-winterbottom-starring-freida-pinto.html }}</ref>。”

