2011年上映的独立制作时代剧《[[黑金_(2011年电影)|黑金]]》（{{lang|en|''Or noir''}}）是这年第三部有平托参演的作品，故事背景设在20世纪30年代的中东地区，一同出演的还有安东尼奥·班德拉斯、[[马克·斯特朗|马克·斯特朗]]和[[莉亚·科贝德|莉亚·科贝德]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto: An actress who has the whole world at her feet | last = Pringle | first = Gill | newspaper = The Independent | date = 2012-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003195749/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/freida-pinto-an-actress-who-has-the-whole-world-at-her-feet-6988643.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/freida-pinto-an-actress-who-has-the-whole-world-at-her-feet-6988643.html}}</ref>。该片获得的整体评价很差<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/day_of_the_falcon/ | title = Day of The Falcon 2013 | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-06-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422055238/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/day_of_the_falcon/}}</ref>，但《纽约时报》的安迪·韦伯斯特（{{lang|en|Andy Webster}}）认为平托和科贝德的演出“令人耳目一新”，称赞两人“独立于这片男性主导且令人窒息的环境之外<ref>{{cite news | last = Webster | first = Andy | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208201101/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/04/movies/jean-jacques-annauds-day-of-the-falcon.html?_r=0 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/04/movies/jean-jacques-annauds-day-of-the-falcon.html?_r=0 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2013-03-02 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | title = Blood Spills Over Black Gold | archivedate = 2015-12-08}}</ref>。”这年大银幕上最后一部平托出演的作品是奇幻片《[[惊天战神|惊天战神]]》，她在片中诠释先知祭司[[淮德拉|淮德拉]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/freida-pinto-takes-on-immortals/650759/ | title = Freida Pinto takes on Immortals | work = The Indian Express | date = 2010-07-23 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-06-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160630144113/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/freida-pinto-takes-on-immortals/650759/}}</ref>。评论界对影片反响不一<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/immortals_2011/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422115831/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/immortals_2011 | title = Immortals (2011) | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-04-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但其全球票房总额达到2亿2690万美元<ref>{{cite web | title = Immortals | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=warofgods.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160428063459/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=warofgods.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-28 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2016-06-30}}</ref>。托德·麦卡锡在《好莱坞报道》发文，称平托对淮德拉的演绎“干练到位”<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404023017/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/immortals-film-review-260279 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/immortals-film-review-260279 | title = Immortals: Film Review | last = McCarthy | first = Todd | work = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2011-11-10 | accessdate = 2016-06-30}}</ref>。

2011年过后，平托连续两年没有新片上映，2013年虽在[[布鲁诺·马尔斯|布鲁诺·马尔斯]]单曲《[[大猩猩_(布鲁诺·马尔斯歌曲)|大猩猩]]》（{{lang|en|''Gorilla''}}）的音乐视频中露面，但却受到[[印度传媒|印度传媒]]批评<ref>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630145744/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/hollywood/news/Freida-Pinto-Hollywood-Slumdog-Millionaire-Gorilla/articleshow/24742229.cms |archivedate=2016-06-30 |deadurl=no |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/hollywood/news/Freida-Pinto-Hollywood-Slumdog-Millionaire-Gorilla/articleshow/24742229.cms? |title=Why did Freida Pinto do pole dance? |last=De |first=Shobhaa |publisher=Mumbai Mirror reprinted by ''The Times of India'' |date=2013-10-26 |accessdate=2016-06-30 }}</ref>。《[[印度时报|印度时报]]》和《[[印度斯坦时报|印度斯坦时报]]》都谴责她在视频内的舞蹈几与“艳舞”无异<ref>{{cite news |newspaper=The Times of India |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/top-10/Bruno-Mars-Gorilla/photostory/33186105.cms |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20140426194050/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/top-10/Bruno-Mars-Gorilla/photostory/33186105.cms |title=Bruno Mars: Gorilla |accessdate=2016-06-30 |archivedate=2014-04-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Goyal | first = Samarth | title = Freida Pinto stuns fans with dirty dancing in Bruno Mars | newspaper = [[印度斯坦时报|Hindustan Times]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055305/http://www.hindustantimes.com/music/freida-pinto-stuns-fans-with-dirty-dancing-in-bruno-mars-video/story-eC3QfbqICCPX04JhVPr74I.html | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | date = 2013-10-17 | url = http://www.hindustantimes.com/music/freida-pinto-stuns-fans-with-dirty-dancing-in-bruno-mars-video/story-eC3QfbqICCPX04JhVPr74I.html}}</ref>。同年，平托还在纪录片《女孩崛起》（{{lang|en|''Girl Rising''}}）中担任讲解员，该片由同名活动组织制作，旨在促进世界各地的女性教育<ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto, Anne Hathaway join Girl Rising documentary | url = http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/freida-pinto-anne-hathaway-join-girl-rising-documentary/1103807/ | work = The Indian Express | date = 2013-04-17 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305154447/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/freida-pinto-anne-hathaway-join-girl-rising-documentary/1103807/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

接下来，平托以2014年的传记片《沙漠舞者》（{{lang|en|''Desert Dancer''}}）回归观众视野，该片主要介绍伊朗编舞家[[阿夫欣·加法朗|阿夫欣·加法朗]]（{{lang|en|Afshin Ghaffarian}}）的人生经历<ref name="KT">{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto: Dancing diva | url = http://www.khaleejtimes.com/article/20150207/ARTICLE/302079987/1002 | work = Khaleej Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305155010/http://www.khaleejtimes.com/article/20150207/ARTICLE/302079987/1002 | date = 2015-02-07 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，她在片中饰演吸食海洛因成瘾的艾拉（{{lang|en|Elaheh}}），是[[瑞斯·里奇|瑞斯·里奇]]（{{lang|en|Reece Ritchie}}）扮演的男主角的意中人<ref name="DD">{{cite news | last = Webster | first = Andy | title = Review: 'Desert Dancer' Tells the Story of the Afshin Ghaffarian | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/10/movies/review-desert-dancer-tells-the-story-of-the-afshin-ghaffarian.html?_r=0 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2015-04-09 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | archivedate = 2015-04-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150422143314/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/10/movies/review-desert-dancer-tells-the-story-of-the-afshin-ghaffarian.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。为了出演这个角色，平托需要连续14个星期每天彩排八小时完成舞蹈训练<ref>{{cite web | last = Joshi | first = Priya | title = Freida Pinto: 'Dance training for Desert Dancer was daunting | url = http://www.digitalspy.com/bollywood/news/a430306/freida-pinto-dance-training-for-desert-dancer-was-daunting/ | publisher = [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] | date = 2012-10-13 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-06-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160609192141/http://www.digitalspy.com/bollywood/news/a430306/freida-pinto-dance-training-for-desert-dancer-was-daunting/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此外，她还在美国的多个康复中心了解毒瘾戒断过程<ref>{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto goes to rehab for her next role | date = 2014-06-06 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120142/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/freida-pinto-rehab-visit-desert-dancer-role/1/365522.html | url = http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/freida-pinto-rehab-visit-desert-dancer-role/1/365522.html | work = India Today | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。电影所获总体评价不佳<ref>{{cite web | title = Desert Dancer (2014) | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/desert-dancer/critic-reviews | publisher = Metacritic | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160316093436/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/desert-dancer/critic-reviews | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Desert Dancer (2014) | archivedate = 2016-05-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160507110617/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/desert_dancer/ | deadurl = no | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/desert_dancer | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2016-06-30}}</ref>，但安迪·韦伯斯特在《纽约时报》发文称平托的角色虽然形象模糊，所涉剧情也非常单薄，但她的表现依然“动人心魄”<ref name="DD" />。

2015年，平托出演的第一部电影是[[泰伦斯·马力克|泰伦斯·马力克]]执导的《[[圣杯骑士|圣杯骑士]]》，影片属[[实验电影|实验电影]]，主要演员包括[[克里斯蒂安·贝尔|克里斯蒂安·贝尔]]、[[凯特·布兰切特|凯特·布兰切特]]、[[娜塔莉·波特曼|娜塔莉·波特曼]]和安东尼奥·班德拉斯<ref>{{cite news | last = O'Falt | first = Chris | title = The Lowdown on Terrence Malick's Three New Films | date = 2014-09-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160508152143/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/what-we-know-terrence-malicks-725908 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/what-we-know-terrence-malicks-725908 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | archivedate = 2016-05-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。她在片中饰演模特海伦（{{lang|en|Helen}}）<ref>{{cite web | last = Mcgovern | first = Joe | title = Wes Bentley discusses Knight of Cups and the Terrence Malick experience | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160415083814/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/03/wes-bentley-terrence-malick-knight-cups | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/03/wes-bentley-terrence-malick-knight-cups | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2016-03-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | archivedate = 2016-04-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Bradshaw | first = Peter | title = Knight of Cups review: Malick's back! With the least interesting spiritual crisis in history | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/08/knight-of-cups-review-film-terrence-malick-christian-bale | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160505062557/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/08/knight-of-cups-review-film-terrence-malick-christian-bale | accessdate = 2016-06-30 | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2015-02-08 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-05-05}}</ref>。谈及此次无剧本演出时，平托表示“第一天时绝对有点伤脑筋，因为你都不知道要干些啥。但只要想通就没关系了，你还会觉得非常轻松。整个过程充满乐趣，令人颇感解放，对此我觉得非常满足。”<ref name="NDTV" />该片在[[第65屆柏林电影节|第65屆柏林电影节]]竞赛单元首映<ref>{{cite web | title = Programme 2015 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202228/http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/2015/02_programm_2015/02_programm_2015.html | publisher = [[柏林电影节|Berlin International Film Festival]] | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/2015/02_programm_2015/02_programm_2015.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Sexton | first = David | title = Berlin Film Festival: Knight of Cups – film review: Christian Bale, Cate Blanchett and Natalie Portman star in Terrence Malick's latest | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085310/http://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/film/berlin-film-festival-knight-of-cups-film-review-christian-bale-cate-blanchett-and-natalie-portman-10044455.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/film/berlin-film-festival-knight-of-cups-film-review-christian-bale-cate-blanchett-and-natalie-portman-10044455.html | work = London Evening Standard | date = 2015-02-13}}</ref>，所获评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/knight_of_cups/?search=knight%20of%20cu | title = Knight of Cups | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422140016/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/knight_of_cups/?search=knight%20of%20cu}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/knight-of-cups | title = Knight of Cups reviews | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160314163204/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/knight-of-cups | publisher = Metacritic | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，再于2016年3月开始在美国上映<ref>{{cite web | title = Christian Bale's 'Knight of Cups' Gets March Release Date | date = 2015-07-23 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160518195458/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/knight-of-cups-release-date-christian-bale-1201547089/ | url = http://variety.com/2015/film/news/knight-of-cups-release-date-christian-bale-1201547089/ | last = McNary | first = Dave | work = Variety | archivedate = 2016-05-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2015年的纪录片《[[万物一体|万物一体]]》（{{lang|en|''Unity''}}）旨在探索地球各物种之间的关系，共有100名讲解员，平托便是其中之一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://variety.com/2015/film/news/documentary-unity-set-for-aug-12-release-with-100-star-narrators-1201477200/ | title = Documentary 'Unity' Set for Aug. 12 Release with 100 Star Narrators | last = McNary | first = Dave | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422092206/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/documentary-unity-set-for-aug-12-release-with-100-star-narrators-1201477200/ | work = Variety | date = 2015-04-22 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-22}}</ref>。这年上映的第三部有她出演的电影是哥伦比亚动作片《[[枪火游戏|枪火游戏]]》（{{lang|en|''Blunt Force Trauma''}}），她在片中饰演一名寻找杀害弟弟凶手的女子，同[[瑞恩·柯万腾|瑞恩·柯万腾]]和[[米基·洛克|米基·洛克]]演对手戏<ref>{{cite web | last = McNary | first = Dave | title = AFM: Ryan Kwanten-Mickey Rourke's 'Blunt Force Trauma' Heads to Voltage | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/ryan-kwanten-blunt-force-trauma-mickey-rourke-1201344710/ | work = Variety | date = 2014-10-31 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503102008/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/ryan-kwanten-blunt-force-trauma-mickey-rourke-1201344710/}}</ref>。《好莱坞报道》的约翰·德福尔对该片观感不佳，批评影片“装模做样，自命不凡<ref>{{cite web | last = DeFore | first = John | title = 'Blunt Force Trauma': Montreal Review | work = The Hollywood Reporter | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/blunt-force-trauma-montreal-review-820902 | date = 2015-09-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004131606/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/blunt-force-trauma-montreal-review-820902 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-04}}</ref>。”2015年5月，據報導，平托將参演[[安迪·瑟克斯|安迪·瑟克斯]]执导的真人冒险奇幻电影《[[森林之子毛克利|森林之子毛克利]]》，该片根据[[魯德亞德·吉卜林|魯德亞德·吉卜林]]的小說《[[叢林奇譚|叢林奇譚]]》改编<ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto reunites with Andy Serkis for Jungle Book: Origins | work = The Indian Express | date = 2015-05-09 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306032313/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/hollywood/freida-pinto-reunites-with-andy-serkis-for-jungle-book-origins/ | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | url = http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/hollywood/freida-pinto-reunites-with-andy-serkis-for-jungle-book-origins/}}</ref>，她在片中为主人翁的养母配音<ref name="NDTV">{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto Filmed Knight of Cups Without a ScriptFreida Pinto Filmed Knight of Cups Without a Script. She Had 'Fun' | archivedate = 2016-05-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://movies.ndtv.com/hollywood/freida-pinto-filmed-knight-of-cups-without-a-script-she-had-fun-1288163 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160527143507/http://movies.ndtv.com/hollywood/freida-pinto-filmed-knight-of-cups-without-a-script-she-had-fun-1288163 | publisher = NDTV | date = 2016-03-17 | accessdate = 2016-07-01}}</ref>。該片於2019年上映<ref name="MowgliNetflix">{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Netflix Acquires Andy Serkis-Directed ‘Mowgli’ From Warner Bros & Plans 2019 Global Streaming Release|url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/netflix-mowgli-deal-andy-serkis-jungle-book-warner-bros-christian-bale-cate-blanchett-benedict-cumberbatch-1202434903/|accessdate=2018-07-27|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2018-07-27|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727184249/https://deadline.com/2018/07/netflix-mowgli-deal-andy-serkis-jungle-book-warner-bros-christian-bale-cate-blanchett-benedict-cumberbatch-1202434903/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

