== 私生活 ==
[[File:FreidaPintoDevPatel08TIFF.jpg|thumb]]

平托从影前曾与她的公关洛汗·安涛（{{lang|en|Rohan Antao}}）订婚，但两人的关系于2009年1月中止，她开始和主演《贫民窟的百万富翁》的戴夫·帕特尔交往，后者比她要小六岁<ref name="USATpintopatel">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141130004522/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2011-03-30-freidaside30_VA_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2011-03-30-freidaside30_VA_N.htm | title = Freida Pinto, Dev Patel: Like something out of a movie | last = Wloszczyna | first = Susan | work = USA Today | date = 2011-03-29 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2014-11-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2012年，平托在接受采访时表示今后不再希望同帕特尔合作演出，因为她觉得两人已无法重现《贫民窟的百万富翁》中那种银幕化学效应<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064232/http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/freida-pinto-wont-act-with-dev-patel-again-6385547.html | url = http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/freida-pinto-wont-act-with-dev-patel-again-6385547.html | title = Freida Pinto won't act with Dev Patel again | work = London Evening Standard | date = 2011-03-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。经过六年交往，两人于2014年12月和平分手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2015/04/06/desert-dancer-freida-pinto/25340953/ |title=Freida Pinto defies expectation for 'Dancer' |work=USA Today |date=2015-04-07 |accessdate=2016-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414083849/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2015/04/06/desert-dancer-freida-pinto/25340953/ |archivedate=2015-04-14 }}</ref>。《贫民窟的百万富翁》获得成功后，平托一度“居无定所”，往返于孟买、伦敦和洛杉矶之间<ref name="Steve" /><ref name="USATpintopatel" /><ref>{{cite news | title = I carry my life in suitcases: Freida Pinto | url = http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/i-carry-my-life-in-suitcases-freida-pinto-597501 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080956/http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/i-carry-my-life-in-suitcases-freida-pinto-597501 | publisher = NDTV | agency = Indo-Asian News Service | date = 2010-11-11 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。不过，她曾于2015年接受《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》采访时表示自己正住在洛杉矶<ref>{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto: Dev Patel And I Are Still Best Friends | date = 2015-04-10 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121154611/http://movies.ndtv.com/hollywood/freida-pinto-dev-patel-and-i-are-still-best-friends-753844 | url = http://movies.ndtv.com/hollywood/freida-pinto-dev-patel-and-i-are-still-best-friends-753844 | publisher = NDTV | archivedate = 2015-11-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

{{quote|quote=在我看来，女性主义就是平等。男人并不比女人高等，反之亦然。许多人对女性主义存在曲解或误解。我们提倡女性主义，但这并非认为应当由女性统治世界，男人只能成为附属。只有在男女公平对待彼此时，我们才有可能拥有逐渐进步的成功国家甚至世界。|source=平托的[[女性主义|女性主义]]立场<ref>{{cite web | title = Feminism is misunderstood: Freida Pinto | work = The Indian Express | date = 2014-12-02 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160409101831/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/feminism-is-misunderstood-frieda-pinto/ | url = http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/feminism-is-misunderstood-frieda-pinto/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-09}}</ref>}}

平托在发展演艺生涯的同时还积极参与人道主义事业，为提高女性及贫困儿童的生活水平代言<ref name="BH">{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto turns producer for women empowerment shows and films | url = http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/17465400/Freida-Pinto-turns-producer-for-women-empowerment-shows-and-films | publisher = Bollywood Hungama | date = 2016-02-26 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404040519/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/17465400/Freida-Pinto-turns-producer-for-women-empowerment-shows-and-films | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Srivastava | first = Priyanka | title = Freida roots for girl rising | url = http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/freida-pinto-roots-for-girl-rising/1/284128.html | work = India Today | date = 2013-06-19 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160407004624/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/freida-pinto-roots-for-girl-rising/1/284128.html}}</ref>。她曾在接受媒体采访时表示，[[安吉丽娜·朱莉|安吉丽娜·朱莉]]和[[马拉拉·优素福扎伊|马拉拉·优素福扎伊]]在女性主义问题上的立场方面对她有“巨大”影响<ref>{{cite web | last = Ramsden | first = Tracy | title = Exclusive: Freida Pinto Talks Feminism, Fame And Angelina Jolie | url = http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/blogs/546946/girl-summit-freida-pinto.html | work = Marie Claire | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404025548/http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/blogs/546946/girl-summit-freida-pinto.html | date = 2014-07-20 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2010年，平托加入[[安德烈·阿加西|安德烈·阿加西]]和[[施特菲·格拉芙|施特菲·格拉芙]]的慈善组织“阿加西基金会”（{{lang|en|the Agassi Foundation}}），还在基金欠款的年度筹款活动“第15届儿童大满贯”中筹得7万5000美元善款，这些款项主要用于向贫困儿童提供教育<ref>{{cite web | title = Freida joins forces with William to raise money for Agassi's charity | date = 2010-10-13 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | url = http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity/freida-joins-forces-with-william-to-raise-money-for-agassi-s-charity_72938.html | publisher = Zee News | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114613/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity/freida-joins-forces-with-william-to-raise-money-for-agassi-s-charity_72938.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Prithwish | last = Ganguly | title = Freida the ace in Agassi-Steffi game | newspaper = The Times of India | date = 2010-09-30 | archivedate = 2015-02-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150228142422/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/news-interviews/Freida-the-ace-in-Agassi-Steffi-game/articleshow/6651134.cms?referral=PM | deadurl = no | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/news-interviews/Freida-the-ace-in-Agassi-Steffi-game/articleshow/6651134.cms?referral=PM | accessdate = 2016-07-01}}</ref>。两年后，她成为[[国际计划组织|国际计划组织]][[因为我是女孩_(慈善运动)|因为我是女孩]]（{{lang|en|Because I am a Girl}}）慈善运动的全球形象大使<ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto bats for girl empowerment in Ethiopia | agency = Indo-Asian News Service | date = 2013-06-02 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | url = http://movies.ndtv.com/hollywood/freida-pinto-bats-for-girl-empowerment-in-ethiopia-633430 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053615/http://movies.ndtv.com/hollywood/freida-pinto-bats-for-girl-empowerment-in-ethiopia-633430 | publisher = NDTV | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>，这项活动的主要目标是帮助数以百万计的女孩摆脱贫困，进而促进[[性别平等|性别平等]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Because I am a girl | archivedate = 2016-06-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160626010957/https://plan-international.org/because-i-am-a-girl | deadurl = no | url = https://plan-international.org/because-i-am-a-girl | publisher = Plan (aid organisation) | accessdate = 2016-07-01}}</ref>。

2013年，平托在为[[古馳|古馳]]“变革的钟声”活动制作的宣传短片中亮相，这项活动旨在筹集资金，呼吁人们关注女性在教育、卫生和社会公正领域面临的问题<ref>{{cite web | date = 2013-04-16 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195348/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/2013/04/16/blake-lively-joins-gucci-chime-for-change---halle-berry-zoe-saldana-beyonce | title = Blake Lively and Halle Berry Join Gucci's Chime For Change | deadurl = no | url = http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/2013/04/16/blake-lively-joins-gucci-chime-for-change---halle-berry-zoe-saldana-beyonce | last = Karmali | first = Sarah | work = Vogue | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。次年，她又在伦敦出席“女孩权利峰会”，呼吁全社会采取更加积极的手段终结[[残割女性生殖器|残割女性生殖器]]和[[童婚|童婚]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Bhattacharya | first = Roshmila | title = Freida Pinto speaks up for girls | date = 2014-07-02 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2014-07-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140724030859/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Freida-Pinto-speaks-up-for-girls/articleshow/38782506.cms | deadurl = no | newspaper = The Times of India | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Freida-Pinto-speaks-up-for-girls/articleshow/38782506.cms}}</ref>。2015年3月，平托发言反对[[印度政府|印度政府]]禁映《[[印度的女儿|印度的女儿]]》之举，这部由[[莱斯莉·乌德温|莱斯莉·乌德温]]（{{lang|en|Leslee Udwin}}）制作的纪录片取材自[[印度黑公交轮奸案|2012年发生在德里的恶性轮奸案]]<ref>{{cite news | title = India's Daughter' gets support from Meryl Streep, Freida Pinto | work = The Indian Express | date = 2015-03-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160611022956/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/entertainment-others/indias-daughter-gets-support-from-meryl-streep-freida-pinto/ | archivedate = 2016-06-11 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | url = http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/entertainment-others/indias-daughter-gets-support-from-meryl-streep-freida-pinto/}}</ref>。《印度的女儿》在美国首映时，她又在接受采访时称应该让公众看到这部绝非意在“羞辱印度的纪录片”<ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto: India should show banned BBC rape documentary | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151231075017/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/11460805/Freida-Pinto-India-should-show-banned-BBC-rape-documentary.html | date = 2015-03-10 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/11460805/Freida-Pinto-India-should-show-banned-BBC-rape-documentary.html | work = The Daily Telegraph | archivedate = 2015-12-31}}</ref>。同年，平托还在另一次接受采访时称：“这部电影绝对不是在宣扬通过暴力来解决问题，事实上我们的理念是要以有史以来最文明的方式来处理这件事<ref>{{cite news | title = India's Daughter documentary receives star-studded premiere in US | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303103410/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/mar/10/indias-daughter-documentary-receives-star-studded-premiere-in-us | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 2015-03-10 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2015/mar/10/indias-daughter-documentary-receives-star-studded-premiere-in-us | newspaper = The Guardian | accessdate = 2016-07-01}}</ref>。”

2016年2月，平托宣布她将加入非营利机构“我们一起干”（{{lang|en|We Do It Together}}），该组织旨在向聚-{焦}-女性权利的剧情电影、纪录片和电视节目提供资金<ref name="BH" />。

