平托在《贫民窟的百万富翁》中出演的只是戏份很少的小角色，但她依然因此获得广泛认可<ref name="Ramachandran">{{cite news | last = Ramachandran | first = S. | title = The star India doesn't want | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304230136/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1111106/jsp/7days/story_14713691.jsp | url = http://www.telegraphindia.com/1111106/jsp/7days/story_14713691.jsp | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | newspaper = The Telegraph (Calcutta) | date = 2011-11-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="IE">{{cite news | title = Proud to see India's representation in Hollywood | newspaper = The Indian Express | date = 2016-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411224915/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/proud-to-see-indias-representation-in-hollywood-freida-pinto/ | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-11 | url = http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/proud-to-see-indias-representation-in-hollywood-freida-pinto/}}</ref>。媒体经常猜测她之后出演的角色及所获片酬<ref name="Steve" /><ref>{{cite web | title = 'I am not famous in India' | url = http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/freida-pinto-i-am-not-famous-in-india/20100823.htm | publisher = Rediff.com | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | date = 2010-08-23 | archivedate = 2016-04-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160405201034/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/freida-pinto-i-am-not-famous-in-india/20100823.htm}}</ref>。2009年3月，《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》宣称平托是收入最高的印度女演员<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823135450/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/5054131/Slumdog-Millionaire-star-Freida-Pinto-is-Bollywood-top-earner.html | last = Nelson | first = Dean | work = The Daily Telegraph | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/5054131/Slumdog-Millionaire-star-Freida-Pinto-is-Bollywood-top-earner.html | title = Slumdog Millionaire star Freida Pinto is Bollywood top earner | date = 2009-03-26 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2015-08-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但她此时还没有出演过[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]电影<ref name="SFgate">{{cite news | url = http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Freida-Pinto-follows-Slumdog-with-Trishna-3686384.php | title = Freida Pinto follows 'Slumdog' with 'Trishna' | last = Stein | first = Ruthe | work = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305083718/http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Freida-Pinto-follows-Slumdog-with-Trishna-3686384.php | date = 2012-07-08 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[CNN-News18|CNN-IBN]]}}电视台一度称平托是“印度对西方的最佳出口”<ref>{{cite web | title = I always dream big: Freida Pinto | url = http://www.news18.com/news/india/i-always-dream-big-freida-pinto-423805.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160427114159/http://www.news18.com/news/india/i-always-dream-big-freida-pinto-423805.html | publisher = CNN-IBN | date = 2011-11-30 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，《加尔各答电信报》则认为她“可以说是印度最闪亮的全球影星<ref name="Ramachandran" />。”

