平托经常在各种杂志举办的美容时尚民意调查中榜上有名<ref>{{cite news | title = Freida Pinto is 'unrecognisable' in Mumbai slums | url = http://www.deccanherald.com/content/120311/freida-pinto-unrecognisable-mumbai-slums.html | agency = Press Trust of India | work = Deccan Herald | date = 2010-12-13 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2015-12-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208164151/http://www.deccanherald.com/content/120311/freida-pinto-unrecognisable-mumbai-slums.html | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Tulshyan | first = Ruchika | title = Freida Pinto: Why Is She A Glamour 'Goddess'? | url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/worldviews/2011/03/30/freida-pinto-why-is-she-a-glamour-goddess/ | work = Forbes | date = 2011-03-30 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111202/http://www.forbes.com/sites/worldviews/2011/03/30/freida-pinto-why-is-she-a-glamour-goddess/#53ad55314987}}</ref>。她曾于2009年入选《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]》杂志一年一度的“世界最美人物”和“世界最佳着装女性”<ref>{{cite web|title=Sneak Peek: World's Most Beautiful People |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222428/http://www.people.com/people/package/gallery/0%2C%2C20267544_20274176_20614653%2C00.html |url=http://www.people.com/people/package/gallery/0,,20267544_20274176_20614653,00.html |work=People |accessdate=2016-07-01 |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | date = 2009-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | url = http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-freida-pinto-winslet-in-people-s-best-dressed-list-1291007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131202232646/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-freida-pinto-winslet-in-people-s-best-dressed-list-1291007 | title = Freida Pinto, Winslet in People's best dressed list | work = Daily News and Analysis | archivedate = 2013-12-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，并于同年入选《[[时尚_(杂志)|时尚]]》杂志的“十大风情女性”<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Hindustan Times | date = 2009-12-24 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065207/http://www.hindustantimes.com/fashion-and-trends/stylish-pinto-in-vogue-s-top-10-list/story-sN31UCEPoKPfp4c2Y5LxMN.html | title = "Stylish" Pinto in Vogue's top 10 list! | deadurl = no | url = http://www.hindustantimes.com/fashion-and-trends/stylish-pinto-in-vogue-s-top-10-list/story-sN31UCEPoKPfp4c2Y5LxMN.html}}</ref>。平托是2011年《洛杉矶时报杂志》（{{lang|en|''Los Angeles Times Magazine''}}）评选的“电影中50位最美丽女性”榜单上唯一的印度女性<ref>{{cite web | title = Freida Pinto more beautiful than Pretty Woman! | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125949/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/freida-pinto-more-beautiful-than-pretty-woman/20110210.htm | url = http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/freida-pinto-more-beautiful-than-pretty-woman/20110210.htm | publisher = Rediff.com | date = 2011-02-10 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。次年，《人物》杂志又将她评为“不论任何年龄段都最美丽的人物”之一<ref>{{cite web|title=2012 Most Beautiful at Every Age – Freida Pinto |url=http://www.people.com/people/package/gallery/0,,20360857_20360861,00.html#20612442 |first=Karen J. |last=Quan |work=People |date=2012-04-20 |accessdate=2016-07-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625070730/http://www.people.com/people/package/gallery/0%2C%2C20360857_20360861%2C00.html |archivedate=2016-06-25 }}</ref>。2010至2012年，她连续三年登上{{lang|en|[[AskMen|AskMen]]}}网站评选的“99位最富魅力女性”排行榜<ref>{{cite web | title = Why She's No.50 | archivedate = 2014-04-29 | publisher = AskMen | accessdate = 2014-04-29 | url = http://www.askmen.com/specials/2010_top_99/freida-pinto-50.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140429103033/http://www.askmen.com/specials/2010_top_99/freida-pinto-50.html | deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Blake Lively Emerges as the Most Desirable Woman of 2011 According to AskMen's 10th Annual Poll | agency = PR Newswire | date = 2011-02-01 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070335/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/blake-lively-emerges-as-the-most-desirable-woman-of-2011-according-to-askmens-10th-annual-poll-115009479.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/blake-lively-emerges-as-the-most-desirable-woman-of-2011-according-to-askmens-10th-annual-poll-115009479.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Sofia Vergara Claims the Title of The Most Desirable Woman of 2012 According to AskMen's 11th Annual Poll | date = 2012-01-31 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074354/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sofia-vergara-claims-the-title-of-the-most-desirable-woman-of-2012-according-to-askmens-11th-annual-poll-138395799.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sofia-vergara-claims-the-title-of-the-most-desirable-woman-of-2012-according-to-askmens-11th-annual-poll-138395799.html | agency = PR Newswire | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

2009年，平托成为巴黎[[萊雅|欧莱雅]]的代言人<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | date = 2013-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120158/http://www.vogue.co.uk/beauty/2013/10/30/blake-lively-new-loreal-paris-global-spokesperson | url = http://www.vogue.co.uk/beauty/2013/10/30/blake-lively-new-loreal-paris-global-spokesperson | title = Blake Lively's Worth It | last = Niven | first = Lisa | work = Vogue | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。两年后，她为欧莱雅产品拍摄的广告引发争议，广告画面显示平托的皮肤似乎更白，效果可能是通过化妆或修图达成。欧莱雅对此否认曾修改平托的照片<ref>{{cite news | date = 2011-09-29 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305012626/http://archive.financialexpress.com/news/freida-pintos-lighter-skin-tone-was-not-altered-says-loreal/853555 | title = Freida Pinto's 'lighter' skin tone was not altered, says L'Oreal | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | url = http://archive.financialexpress.com/news/freida-pintos-lighter-skin-tone-was-not-altered-says-loreal/853555 | work = The Financial Express }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.telegraphindia.com/1110929/jsp/frontpage/story_14567118.jsp | title = Freida fairer? Not fair – L'Oreal denies buzz that actor's skin-tone was lightened in ad | last = Roy | first = Amit | work = The Telegraph | date = 2011-09-29 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304212753/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1110929/jsp/frontpage/story_14567118.jsp}}</ref>。

平托在好莱坞已颇具人气，还在印度却相对籍籍无名<ref name="Ramachandran" /><ref>{{cite web | last = Ramachandran | first = Naman | url = http://travel.cnn.com/mumbai/life/curious-case-freida-pinto-966707/ | title = The curious case of Freida Pinto | work = CNN | date = 2011-08-26 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-04-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160407164920/http://travel.cnn.com/mumbai/life/curious-case-freida-pinto-966707/}}</ref>，许多评论家和分析人员认为这是因为《贫民窟的百万富翁》在印度不受待见<ref>{{cite news | title = I can find my place in Bollywood now: Freida Pinto | newspaper = The Indian Express | date = 2013-03-16 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307054120/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/i-can-find-my-place-in-bollywood-now-freida-pinto/1088643/0 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/i-can-find-my-place-in-bollywood-now-freida-pinto/1088643/0}}</ref>。印度[[社会学|社会学家]][[阿希斯·南迪|阿希斯·南迪]]（{{lang|en|Ashis Nandy}}）称自己压根儿就没发现她，该国新闻工作者[[哈立德·穆罕默德|哈立德·穆罕默德]]（{{lang|en|Khalid Mohamed}}）也认为平托还没有在孟买取得一席之地<ref name="Ramachandran" />。印度媒体批评她无论是说[[印地语|印地语]]还是说英语的口音都不稳定，觉得她是因皮肤黝黑而无法获得出演宝莱坞电影的机会<ref name="Steve" />。受到此类批评的同时，也有媒体称赞平托在好莱坞经常出演不同国籍的人物，没有落入印度人物千篇一律的[[刻板印象|刻板形象]]<ref name="roles" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Stereotyping a lesser evil in Indian cinema: Freida Pinto | url = http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/stereotyping-a-lesser-evil-in-indian-cinema-freida-pinto/1/260878.html | work = India Today | date = 2013-04-05 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2015-10-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004183459/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/stereotyping-a-lesser-evil-in-indian-cinema-freida-pinto/1/260878.html}}</ref>。2012年，平托本人在接受《印度斯坦时报》采访时表示，她一直都在着力避开落入刻板印象的角色<ref>{{cite news | last = Nayar Singh | first = Anjuri | title = Freida won't play girl who wears sari, bindi | url = http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/freida-won-t-play-girl-who-wears-sari-bindi/story-0LItHGPKSqoNbp9UMeTxZN.html | newspaper = Hindustan Times | date = 2014-12-18 | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055111/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/freida-won-t-play-girl-who-wears-sari-bindi/story-0LItHGPKSqoNbp9UMeTxZN.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

出演“高成本好莱坞大片”的同时，平托还会选择“聪明的独立电影”，在两者间寻找平衡。面对有关她为什么更倾向出演好莱坞电影的问题，平托回答：“我只是想当演员。身为演员，你无需把自身局限在某种文化或种族以内。我希望能前去每一个地方，也愿意接受世界上任何地方的拍片邀约。”<ref name="DNA">{{cite news | last = Guha | first = Aniruddha | title = What's ethnicity got to do with bagging Hollywood films? asks Freida Pinto | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160702061845/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-what-s-ethnicity-got-to-do-with-bagging-hollywood-films-asks-freida-pinto-1578006 | work = Daily News and Analysis | date = 2011-08-20 | url = http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-what-s-ethnicity-got-to-do-with-bagging-hollywood-films-asks-freida-pinto-1578006 | accessdate = 2016-07-02 | archivedate = 2016-07-02}}</ref>

